descriptionHtml:
Invest in the US stock market.
More than 5,000 stocks and ETF available for you to buy and sell stocks in the US market without paying trading fees and without minimum deposits.

At Hapi we want to democratize access to the US stock market so that anyone in Latam can buy and sell stocks and ETF easily and safe. Invest in stocks without paying commissions
Open your account for free, we do not charge account maintenance or stock trading fees.

Start with the amount you want
Start your investment portfolio with the amount that makes you feel comfortable. Start with as little as from US$1.

Buy fractional shares
With fractional shares you can own a portion of a stocks or ETF of the brands you love. At Hapi there are thousands of different stocks and ETF for you to choose from.

Invest in the US safely
Hapi is a broker dealer regulated and supervised by Finra and the SEC, where your assets are protected for up to USD 500,000 by SIPC.

Achieve financial freedom
At Hapi we work so that anyone from LATAM can invest in the US stock market easily, quickly and safe.

Sign up in minutes, enter the amount of funds you want, and start investing!


About Hapi

Hapi Corp. (“Hapi”) is an SEC registered broker-dealer, a member of the Financial Industry Regulatory Authority (“FINRA”) (CRD number 311868), and Securities Investor Protection Corporation (“SIPC”), which protects securities of its members customers for up to US$ 500,000 (including US$ 250,000 in cash). For additional information visit SIPC Please note, SIPC covers the return of your securities should Hapi become insolvent, not against the decline of your securities. Click here for Hapi’s form CRS (please link), which describes Hapi’s products and services and here for Hapi’s record on FINRA’s BrokerCheck website

Hapi is a company incorporated and operated in the United States of America. It is the client's responsibility to ascertain the legal requirements that the current legal framework applicable in its country of residence establishes about the services provided by Hapi, as well as to ascertain whether the current legal framework applicable in its country of residence allows using the services provided by Hapi. This is not an offer, solicitation of an offer, or advice to buy or sell securities, or open a brokerage account in any jurisdiction where Hapi is not registered, or Hapi’s operations contravene local laws.

Hapi offers commission free trading. However, certain SEC, FINRA, or account fees may apply to certain products, operations and investments. Please refer to our full fee schedule.

All investments involve risk, including the loss of capital. Hapi offers self directed investment accounts for those investors who feel comfortable managing their own investments. For a full list of our disclosures, please visit our disclosures page.
